le a ten times larger power: ����⁢/��SQL≃1/√��*=10. Squeezed⁢varational—��⁢=1.3(��−2⁢��⁢��*)1/4≃0.24 and ��≃80 using ����⁢/��SQL=1; and ��≃(��−2⁢��⁢��*)1/4≃0.18 and ��≃180 using ����⁢/��SQL=√��−2⁢��/��*≃3.2.},
  number = {2},
  urldate = {2024-07-23},
  journal = {Physical Review D},
  author = {Kimble, H. J. and Levin, Yuri and Matsko, Andrey B. and Thorne, Kip S. and Vyatchanin, Sergey P.},
